Package edu.sjsu.assignment2

Class myTime

java.lang.Object
edu.sjsu.assignment2.myTime
public class myTime extends Object
myTime class contains methods to prints the time difference between the two input times, and to validate inputs. If the first time is later than the second time, assume the second time is the next day.

    • validTimeInput

      public static boolean validTimeInput(String str)
      This method is for time input validation. The input has to be a positive 4-digit integer in format hhmm(h - hour; m - minute)
      Parameters:
      str - the String time input
      Returns:
      true if the input is validated
